Installation:

Clone git repo to ~/Documents/dotfiles/

programs: scrot amixer playerctl xclip

~/.xsessionrc runs init.sh
overwrite ~/.bashrc with .bashrc
copy Roboto Mono font to ~/.local/share/fonts and rebuild font cache (fc-cache -fv)
check dwm/config.h and make sure screenshot path is correct
check init.sh and make sure FILES is set correctly
compile dwm, st, dmenu, slstatus and ly
copy dwm.desktop to /usr/share/xsessions/dwm.desktop
install ly

remap caps lock to right shift /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/pc


git://git.suckless.org/dwm
git://git.suckless.org/dmenu
git://git.suckless.org/st
git://git.suckless.org/slstatus
https://github.com/nullgemm/ly.git
